data.name: FilterEvent
desc: is an event fired by a filter controller, when the filter managed by the controller changes.

items.name: DisjunctiveTerm
lines: denotes the index of the disjunctive term to which the event applies, if any.

items.name: FilterComponent
lines: denotes the index of the filter component to which the event applies, if any.

items.name: PredicateExpression
lines: denotes the predicate expression associated with the event.
